Constraints.name: mom
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: Bx
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: Bx*mom/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: Bx
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: -mom*(Bx**2/(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) - 1)/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: By
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: By*mom/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: By
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: -mom*(By**2/(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) - 1)/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: Bz
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: Bz*mom/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)

Constraints.name: Bz
Constraints.derivative_lambda: lambda args : (lambda mom,Bx,By,Bz: -mom*(Bz**2/(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) - 1)/np.sqrt(Bx**2 + By**2 + Bz**2) )(*args)
